For our many readers looking for all-cotton clothing, we have an additional 
source: Deva, Box S-89, Burkittsville, Md. 21718, is an 11-year-old cottage 
industry, with all-cotton products crafted locally by home-based stitchers who 
sew their names into the garments they make. Everything is unconditionally 
guaranteed. Send for a catalogue. The toll-free number is (800) 222-8024. 
</P>
