CYPRESS DEFEATS IRVINE IN METRO LEAGUE GAME 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The Cypress Dawgs defeated the Irvine Metros, 11-0, in a Metro League baseball 
game Wednesday at UC Irvine. 
</P>
<P>
Jim Delehoy pitched a four-hitter and struck out seven. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
