Brinker of Newport Beach, right, won with $42,300 bid for a Tustin house. ; 
Photo, Bidders and spectators alike pack Santa Ana auditorium for an IRS 
auction. ; Photo, Dod Bateman of Irvine bids on a San Juan Capistrano home. ; 
Photo, Paul Osborne of Irvine checks properties to be auctioned. ADRIENNE 
HELITZER / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
