county resolution Tuesday to Ralph Opacic, Orange County High School of the 
Arts director, and Howard Prouty, president of the Los Alamitos school's 
Foundation, a private support group. The resolution honors the school on the 
completion of its second academic year. Wieder gave the Foundation a check for 
$5,000 in federal revenue sharing funds. RICK PERRY / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
